snippet.title: Devoid Prototype Gameplay Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Fight, Mine, Scavenge, Trade, Craft or Mission your way through the Anadeia Galaxy as you explore synergies of different skills, ships, weapons and equipment alone or on the couch with a friend in this approachable space sandbox.
Check it out on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2312650/Devoid_Prototype/
Join the Discord: 
https://discord.com/invite/kXDd78TjWj
